Haider, who has already stated that he is ready to collaborate with any party and that he planned the return to Vienna, on the national political scene, apparently put on this evolution.
The last party to have access to the parliament is the Greens, but these have slightly lost and fell back, among the Austrian political parties, from the third to the fifth place.
